summary: Oblivious deer says, "there is no river."
descriptionHtml:
NOW PART OF THE [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/46495/?]SKYTEST INTEGRATION PROJECT[/url]



CANNOT BE USED WITH THE LITE VERSION OF SKYTEST, CANNOT BE USED WITH THE ESM VERSION OF SKYTEST

This mod edits 255 Realistic Wildlife Skyrim variants, giving them skytest ai packages, factions, and combat styles. Also edits their stats, aggro radius, and behavior to resemble skytest variants.

The purpose of this mod is to make RWS creatures on par with Skytest ones and to increase immersion.



Load Order

Real Wildlife Skyrim.esp
Skytest Realistic Animals and Predators.esp
Skytest Real Wildlife Skyrim.esp

Use a batched/merged patch to merge leveled item records.

Credits

Nedius for RWS
Etayorius for Skytest
